---- 10.txt -----
SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2008
AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'computer-animated-movie',
'female-nudity',
'based-on-novel',
'second-part',
'based-on-comic',
'tv-special',
'violence',
'hospital',
'tv-special');
-----------------------------
(((((((((((ci chn) mk) mi_idx) t) kt) k) cc) n) it2) cct1) cct2)
(((((((((((ci chn) mk) mi_idx) t) kt) k) cc) n) it2) cct1) cct2)
rtos cost 628666.26
tables
['ci', 'chn', 'mk', 'mi_idx', 't', 'kt', 'k', 'cc', 'n', 'it2', 'cct1', 'cct2']

---- 1000.txt -----
SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Sci-Fi',
'Action')
AND t.production_year > 2001;
-----------------------------
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)
rtos cost 956175.75

---- 10001.txt -----
SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('hand-to-hand-combat',
'blood',
'based-on-comic');
-----------------------------
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
rtos cost 987708.86
tables
['mi', 'mk', 'k', 'mc', 't', 'cn', 'ci', 'n', 'chn', 'an', 'it', 'rt']

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Crime',
'Drama',
'Family',
'Thriller',
'War',
'Horror')
AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'murder',
'tv-special',
'10,000-mile-club',
'fight',
'violence',
'fish-tank')
AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(written by)');

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('War',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;
-----------------------------

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'fight',
'murder',
'ancient-china')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1998
AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'blood',
'violence',
'superhero',
'magnet',
'sequel',
'gore',
'tv-special',
'fight',
'sequel');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'martial-arts',
'violence',
'female-nudity',
'laser',
'sequel',
'laser',
'fight',
'magnet',
'murder')
AND t.production_year > 2000;

       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Thriller',
'Drama',
'Sci-Fi',
'Horror',
'Action',
'Action')
AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'fight',
'marvel-comics',
'laser',
'female-nudity',
'sequel',
'dragging-a-dead-body')
AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)',
'(written by)');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'violence',
'fight',
'preparation')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

  AND mc.company_id = cn.id

  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id

AND cct1.kind IN ('cast',
'crew')

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2005
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'martial-arts',

       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('War',
'Action')
AND t.production_year > 2001;
-----------------------------
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('American',
'Denish',
'Germany',
'English',
'Swedish',
'Bulgaria',
'German',
'Danish',
'Crime')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2007;
-----------------------------
(((((((((((lt ml) mk) t) mi) mc) ct) cc) k) cn) cct1) cct2)
(((((((((((lt ml) mk) t) mi) mc) ct) cc) k) cn) cct1) cct2)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'violence',
'web');
-----------------------------
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
rtos cost 987708.86
tables
['mi', 'mk', 'k', 'mc', 't', 'cn', 'ci', 'n', 'chn', 'an', 'it', 'rt']

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;
-----------------------------

(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1997
AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'murder',
'marvel-comics',
'tv-special');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id

     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,

     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('Denmark',
'German',
'Sweden',
'English',
'Swedish',
'Danish',
'American',
'Germany',
'Sweden:90')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2013;

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')

     comp_cast_type AS cct2,

     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

                  '(head writer)',

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('gore',
'second-part',
'fight',
'tv-special',
'female-nudity',
'violence',
'based-on-comic',
'superhero',
'revenge',
'tv-special')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id

  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2010
AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Danish',
'Norwegian',
'Crime')
AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('hospital',
'death',
'murder');

(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1995
AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'murder-in-title',
'superhero',
'murder');

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND mi.info IN ('War',
'Horror',
'Family',
'Action',
'Thriller',
'Crime')
AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'hero',

'camp-counselor')
AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',

'(producer)',
'(written by)');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('female-nudity',
'martial-arts',
'fight');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'murder-in-title',
'tv-special');

(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year = 1998
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Norwegian',
'Denish',
'Danish',
'When the police reveal a narcotic smuggling the driver is shot dead. It appears that the driver is Superintendent Martin Beck''s son. Beck breaks down and moves out of the way. But on his colleagues request he returns.');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('fight',
'web',
'tv-special',
'hospital',
'marvel-comics',
'violence',
'sequel',
'superhero',
'fight',
'computer-animated-movie')
AND t.production_year > 2006;
-----------------------------
(((((((((((ci chn) mi_idx) mk) it2) t) kt) k) cc) n) cct1) cct2)
(((((((((((ci chn) mi_idx) mk) it2) t) kt) k) cc) n) cct1) cct2)

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2004
AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-novel',
'fight',
'based-on-comic',
'murder');

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year = 1998
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('German',
'Sweden',
'America',
'Denmark');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'violence',
'superhero',
'death-of-mother')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

(((((((((((mk mi) k) t) mc) ci) chn) n) rt) an) it) cn)

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Sci-Fi',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;
-----------------------------
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)
(((((((((((it1 mi) ci) mi_idx) mk) it2) k) n) cc) cct1) t) cct2)

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('Germany',
'American',
'English',
'Norway',
'Swedish',
'USA',
'Danish',
'Bulgaria',
'RAT:1.85 : 1')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2013;

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,

     cast_info AS ci,

  AND it2.info = 'votes'

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2008
AND k.keyword IN ('hero',
'second-part',
'sequel',
'blood');

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year = 1997
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Denish',
'Sweden',
'Norwegian',
'Sweden:31 October 1997');

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('War',
'Crime')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id

  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete+verified',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;
-----------------------------

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1998
AND k.keyword IN ('blood',
'superhero',
'superhero',
'laser');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'blood',
'sequel');

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'violence',
'gore',
'party')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
-----------------------------

(((((((((((mk mi) k) t) mc) ci) chn) n) rt) an) it) cn)

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('Germany',
'Denish',
'American',
'English',
'Swedish',

'Swedish')

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('cast',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Crime',
'Crime')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('character-name-in-title',
'claw',
'murder',
'kung-fu-classic')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2002
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'web',
'fight',
'violence');

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('German',
'Denmark',
'Danish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'Bulgaria',
'English',
'Norway',
'Crime')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2008;

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'Thriller',
'Drama',
'Crime',
'Sci-Fi',
'Horror')

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Western',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1997
AND k.keyword IN ('magnet',
'computer-animated-movie',
'laser',
'hospital',
'death',
'superhero',
'second-part',
'violence',
'sequel',
'based-on-comic');

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2000
AND mi.info IN ('American',
'Germany',
'Norway',
'Norway')
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'crew');

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,

       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'death',
'web',
'marvel-comics',
'magnet',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'death',
'fight',
'web',
'second-part')
AND t.production_year > 1995;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'blood',
'hospital');
-----------------------------
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
(((((((((((mi mk) k) mc) t) cn) ci) n) chn) an) it) rt)
rtos cost 987708.86

['mi', 'mk', 'k', 'mc', 't', 'cn', 'ci', 'n', 'chn', 'an', 'it', 'rt']

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('magnet',
'female-nudity',
'based-on-comic',
'banquet')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
