SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Danish',
'Denish',
'Bulgaria',
'Swedish',
'German',
'Norway',
'USA',
'Norway')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2006;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'web',
'tv-special',
'tough-girl')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

(((((((((((mk mi) k) t) mc) ci) chn) n) rt) an) it) cn)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1994

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year = 1997
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete+verified',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Norwegian',
'Norway',
'German');

       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,

     name AS n,

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('hand-to-hand-combat',
'hero',
'murder');

       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('American',
'Norwegian',
'USA',
'Sweden',
'Danish',
'English',
'America',
'Denish',
'Sweden')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2012;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'violence',
'sequel',
'dojo')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Thriller',
'Drama',
'Sci-Fi',
'Action',
'Crime',
'Crime')
AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND k.keyword IN ('tv-special',
'based-on-comic',
'hand-to-hand-combat',
'tv-special',

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2002
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'martial-arts',
'fight',
'death');

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
AND mi.info IN ('Denish',
'Sweden',

'America',

'Germany')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2003;

WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('blood',
'murder-in-title',
'superhero',
'web',
'murder',
'sequel',
'revenge',
'gore',
'murder',
'magnet')
AND t.production_year > 1995;

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'
  AND cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2012
AND mi.info IN ('Danish',
'Norwegian',
'English',
'Crime')
AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'crew');

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like '%Johnson,%';

       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_movie_dubbed
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'

       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,

     name AS n,

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'War',
'Action',
'Family',
'Thriller',
'Sci-Fi')
AND n.gender = 'm';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND t.production_year > 2008;
-----------------------------
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Sci-Fi',
'Drama')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.3'
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2004;
-----------------------------

((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'budget'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND n.name like '%Johnson,%';

SELECT MIN(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM aka_name AS a1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND a1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[de]'
AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%Rylan)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[nl]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)',
'(voice)')
AND mi.info IN ('Family',
'War',
'Drama',
'Crime',
'Thriller',
'Sci-Fi')
AND n.gender = 'm';
-----------------------------

((((((mi_idx ci) t) mi) it2) it1) n)

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like '%W%';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(as%'
AND cn.country_code = '[nl]'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SELECT MIN(an1.name) AS actress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_movie_dubbed
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND n1.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n1.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.note = '(as Dr. Yoshiro Nakamats)'
AND rt.role = 'actor';
-----------------------------
((((((n1 an1) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
((((((n1 an1) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%Marcy%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND t.production_year > 2009;
-----------------------------
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)
rtos cost 562874.0

SELECT MIN(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM aka_name AS a1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND a1.person_id = ci.person_id

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'budget'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND n.name like '%Alex%';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%Rylan)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[ca]'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,

     company_type AS ct,

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like '%Johnson,%';

       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_movie_dubbed
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'

  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'

     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like '%S%';

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)')
AND mi.info IN ('Family',
'Western')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2007;
-----------------------------
((((((mi_idx ci) t) mi) it2) it1) n)
((((((mi_idx ci) t) mi) it2) it1) n)
rtos cost 901167.07
tables
['mi_idx', 'ci', 't', 'mi', 'it2', 'it1', 'n']

SELECT MIN(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM aka_name AS a1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND a1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[ru]'
AND rt.role = 'writer';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND t.production_year > 2008;
-----------------------------
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) rt) chn)

SQL : SELECT MIN(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM aka_name AS a1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND a1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[jp]'
AND rt.role = 'writer';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[gb]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2008;
-----------------------------
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) chn) rt)
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) chn) rt)

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'composer'
AND t.title like 'Ghost%'
AND ci.note = '(music by)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2003  AND 2007;
-----------------------------
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
rtos cost 588439.98
tables
['an', 'n', 'ci', 't', 'mc', 'cn', 'rt']

     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'

       MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like 'J%';

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'actor'
AND t.title like 'Shout%'
AND ci.note = '(voice: English version)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2006;

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND mi.info IN ('Drama',
'War')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.4'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2013;
-----------------------------
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
rtos cost 900395.18

     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,

       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id

AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

SELECT MIN(an1.name) AS costume_designer_pseudo,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_costumes
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[jp]'
AND rt.role = 'actor';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[ca]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2008;
-----------------------------
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) chn) rt)
((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) chn) rt)
rtos cost 563952.77

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)')
AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Family',
'Western',
'Crime',
'Sci-Fi',
'Drama')
AND n.gender = 'm';
-----------------------------
((((((mi_idx ci) t) mi) it2) it1) n)
((((((mi_idx ci) t) mi) it2) it1) n)
rtos cost 944304.23

FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew'
AND t.title like 'X-Men:%'
AND ci.note = '(script supervisor: splinter unit)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2004  AND 2012;
-----------------------------

((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'War')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.2'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2001;
-----------------------------
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
rtos cost 900083.45
tables
['it1', 'mi', 'mi_idx', 'ci', 'it2', 't', 'n']
leading_list

mcts: 0.07617306709289551 plan gen: 0.001565 MPHE: 0.005500078201293945 hinter latency: 6.392100999999999

  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%Marcy%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')

'Thriller')

SELECT MIN(an1.name) AS actress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_movie_dubbed
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND n1.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n1.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(as%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_american_movie,
       MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Crime')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.6'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2009;
-----------------------------
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
rtos cost 900071.38

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'writer'
AND t.title like 'The%'
AND ci.note = '(based on the novel by)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1978  AND 2013;
-----------------------------
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
rtos cost 588439.95

       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer

     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(as%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2009;
-----------------------------

((((((mc ct) t) cn) ci) chn) rt)
rtos cost 570431.63

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'budget'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(uncredited)')
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND n.name like '%Angel%';
-----------------------------
((((((ci n) mi_idx) t) it2) mi) it1)
((((((ci n) mi_idx) t) it2) mi) it1)
rtos cost 817386.51

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'editor'
AND t.title like 'Suspicion%'
AND ci.note = '(as Ron E. Yoshida)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2004;
-----------------------------
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
((((((an n) ci) t) mc) cn) rt)
rtos cost 588439.98

['an', 'n', 'ci', 't', 'mc', 'cn', 'rt']

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'budget'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(executive producer)')
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND n.name like '%Smith,%';

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND mi.info IN ('Thriller',
'Drama')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.6'
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2006  AND 2011;
-----------------------------
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
((((((it1 mi) mi_idx) ci) it2) t) n)
rtos cost 900387.82

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS russian_mov_with_actor_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(as%'
AND cn.country_code = '[ca]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_american_movie,
       MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like 'J%'
AND cn.country_code = '[de]';

SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'director'
AND t.title like 'Raki%'
AND ci.note = '(episode director) (as IchirÃ´ Miyoshi)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'writer'
AND t.title like 'Sukai%'
AND ci.note = '(episode writer) (as Takawo Yoshioka)'

SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie,
       MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.name like 'A%';

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'budget'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(producer)')
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND n.name like '%Williams,%';
-----------------------------
((((((ci n) mi_idx) t) it2) mi) it1)
((((((ci n) mi_idx) t) it2) mi) it1)

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND t.production_year > 2008;

       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL

  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'

'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)',
'(writer)',

SELECT MIN(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM aka_name AS a1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND a1.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[ru]'
AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew';

SELECT MIN(an1.name) AS actress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_movie_dubbed
FROM aka_name AS an1,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an1.person_id = n1.id
  AND n1.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an1.person_id = ci.person_id

  AND n1.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'

SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Thriller',
'Crime',
'War',
'Horror',
'Action',
'Drama')
AND n.gender = 'm';

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
FROM char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%(voice)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SELECT Count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'height'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.gender = 'f'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2001  AND 2011;

SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

  AND t.id = cc.movie_id

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,

     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

  AND it3.info = 'height'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id

  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2012;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2012;
-----------------------------
((((((((((((((((it mi) mk) k) mc) cn) cc) cct1) ci) n) chn) rt) pi) it3) t) an) cct2)
((((((((((((((((it mi) mk) k) mc) cn) cc) cct1) ci) n) chn) rt) pi) it3) t) an) cct2)
rtos cost 1063799.22
tables
['it', 'mi', 'mk', 'k', 'mc', 'cn', 'cc', 'cct1', 'ci', 'n', 'chn', 'rt', 'pi', 'it3', 't', 'an', 'cct2']
leading_list
['/*+Leading(it mi)*/']
real time: 5573.853
pg plan: 0.07875 pg run: 5.573853
totalTime: 231931.20799999998
mcts: 2.2643799781799316 plan gen: 0.07875 MPHE: 0.01656794548034668 hinter latency: 5.573853

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2002;

SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'

  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id

  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2003  AND 2013;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2002  AND 2013;
-----------------------------

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Al%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2010;

SQL : SELECT Count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'height'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2006  AND 2011;

---- 11851.txt -----
SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Br%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2009;
-----------------------------
((((((((((((((((it mi) mk) k) t) mc) cc) cct1) ci) n) chn) cn) rt) pi) an) it3) cct2)
((((((((((((((((it mi) mk) k) t) mc) cc) cct1) ci) n) chn) cn) rt) pi) an) it3) cct2)

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
