     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Wi%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2009;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000  AND 2010;

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2002  AND 2012;

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

                  '(voice: English version)')

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id

  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Br%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2008;

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

     person_info AS pi,

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2001;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Br%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2009;

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Wi%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2005;
-----------------------------

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'height'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2010;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Wi%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2001  AND 2009;

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

                  '(voice: English version)')

SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2001  AND 2012;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2005;

     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'

  AND it.info = 'release dates'

  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id

  AND n.id = pi.person_id

  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2013;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Le%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2011;

SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Wi%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000  AND 2012;
-----------------------------

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id

SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2007;

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,

     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',

     movie_keyword AS mk,

     person_info AS pi,

     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2012;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2008;

     movie_info AS mi,

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'

SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2013;

     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2008;

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

  AND it3.info = 'height'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
